                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "fbovi",
                  "fill": "$inkMuted",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Led CMI’s tech transformation - scaled the remote-first team 4→10 while owning release workflow end-to-end. Cut post-release bugs ~60% and installed hiring, coaching, and quality practices that stuck. Craft: Dockerized onboarding (weeks → 1 day), LAMP platform serving hundreds of millions in monthly assets.",
