                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "lDBHQ",
                  "fill": "$inkMuted",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "First front-end hire at Canada’s first regulated crypto marketplace; promoted twice. Led Vue→React/Gatsby→Next.js migration - ~50% faster deploys, ~70% faster renders - while managing delivery through Kanban→sprints. Craft: Amplify CI/CD, Cypress, Sentry, PR review.",
