              "width": "fill_container",
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 18,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "qCUMQ",
                  "fill": "$inkMuted",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "I’ve spent my career close to the work - first as a hands-on developer, then leading remote-first teams through the messy middle of scaling. I care about the same things at every level: does the team ship confidently, and does the bar keep rising?",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "N4oMnQ",
                  "fill": "$inkMuted",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "At CMI I led a tech transformation, grew the team, and cut post-release bugs while making onboarding a one-day exercise. At Bitbuy - Canada’s first regulated crypto marketplace - I was the first front-end hire, promoted twice, and led platform migrations that made deploys faster and safer through a $206M acquisition.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "XGjaG",
                  "fill": "$inkMuted",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "I lead from the front. I diagnose the real constraint before prescribing, install systems that stick, and measure the outcomes teams actually feel. I’m most useful when an org needs an improver, not a maintainer.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
